        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1003150978" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10315888199985418277">Enchanting, lyrical, rhythmic are all words I would use to describe Kate Forsyth&apos;s prose in BITTER GREENS. I read this novel at precisely the right time--when my schedule was overly busy, my stress levels high, and so much of the world seemed dark--a time when I needed the exquisite escape of a beautiful novel. I look forward to reading much more by this author.</span>
  <span id="freeText10315888199985418277" style="display:none">Enchanting, lyrical, rhythmic are all words I would use to describe Kate Forsyth's prose in BITTER GREENS. I read this novel at precisely the right time--when my schedule was overly busy, my stress levels high, and so much of the world seemed dark--a time when I needed the exquisite escape of a beautiful novel. I look forward to reading much more by this author.</span>
